<html lang="es">
  <head>
    <meta charset="utf-8" />
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1" />
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="/src/styles/global.css" />
    <title>Opposite-Me</title>
    <style>
      body {
        background-color: #111827; /* bg-gray-900 */
        min-height: 100vh; /* min-h-screen */
        font-family: sans-serif; /* font-sans */
        color: #e5e7eb; /* text-gray-200 */
      }
      
      main {
        width: 100%; /* w-full */
        max-width: 56rem; /* max-w-4xl */
        margin-left: auto; /* mx-auto */
        margin-right: auto; /* mx-auto */
        padding: 4rem 1rem; /* py-16 px-4 */
        display: flex; /* flex */
        flex-direction: column; /* flex-col */
        align-items: center; /* items-center */
      }
      
      .back-button {
        border: 1px solid white; /* border border-white */
        width: 80px; /* w-[80px] */
        cursor: pointer; /* cursor-pointer */
        margin-bottom: 0.625rem; /* mb-2.5 */
        font-size: 18px; /* text-[18px] */
      }
      
      .card {
        background-color: #1f2937; /* bg-gray-800 */
        border-radius: 0.75rem; /* rounded-xl */
        overflow: hidden; /* overflow-hidden */
        box-shadow: 0 20px 25px -5px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1), 0 10px 10px -5px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.04); /* shadow-xl */
        border: 1px solid #374151; /* border border-gray-700 */
        width: 100%; /* w-full */
        max-width: 600px; /* max-w-[600px] */
        margin-left: auto; /* mx-auto */
        margin-right: auto; /* mx-auto */
      }
      
      .image-container {
        height: 400px; /* h-[400px] */
        overflow: hidden; /* overflow-hidden */
      }
      
      .card-image {
        width: 100%; /* w-full */
        height: 100%; /* h-full */
        object-fit: cover; /* object-cover */
        object-position: top; /* object-top */
        transition: all 0.5s; /* transition-all duration-500 */
      }
      
      .card-image:hover {
        transform: scale(1.05); /* hover:scale-105 */
      }
      
      .card-content {
        padding: 1.5rem; /* p-6 */
      }
      
      .card-text {
        color: #e5e7eb; /* text-gray-200 */
        font-size: 1.125rem; /* text-lg */
      }
    </style>
  </head>
  <body>
    <main>
      <a href="/"><button type="button" class="back-button">Go Back</button></a>
      <div class="card">
        <div class="image-container">
          <img
            src="/images/beto.jpg"
            alt="Descripción de la imagen"
            class="card-image"
          />
        </div>
        <div class="card-content">
          <p class="card-text">
            He is my friend José Alberto, but everyone in our friend group calls him 'Beto.' I chose him as my opposite because he always makes everyone laugh, while I'm more of the person who just stays in the group to laugh. I don't usually talk much; I have trouble speaking. I used to have speech problems when I was little, and it stuck with me.
            I included him because he knows how to express himself very well, which is something I barely do because I get very nervous.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </main>
  </body>
</html>